{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/my-chromebook-review/","webpackCompilationHash":"55513de83e71e41db443","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":{"name":"Joey Xie","contacts":{"twitter":"xf_joey"}},"disqusShortname":"joeyxf-com","subtitle":"每天进步一点点","title":"Joey的博客","url":"https://joeyxf.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ef8081b1-2107-5182-a570-49ff0601acb9","html":"<p>今年2月份附近入手的一台二手chromebook，到目前为止已经用了很长一段时间了，打算写一篇文章来总结一下使用体验。</p>\n<p>先来看看我的屏幕截图，目前看起来还觉得挺geek的\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fa35a8237fdc03f0f8f6187e1dad0a42/95139/chromebook-htop.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.22254758418741%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"终端\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/fa35a8237fdc03f0f8f6187e1dad0a42/f570d/chromebook-htop.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fa35a8237fdc03f0f8f6187e1dad0a42/0783d/chromebook-htop.png 240w,\n/static/fa35a8237fdc03f0f8f6187e1dad0a42/782f4/chromebook-htop.png 480w,\n/static/fa35a8237fdc03f0f8f6187e1dad0a42/f570d/chromebook-htop.png 960w,\n/static/fa35a8237fdc03f0f8f6187e1dad0a42/95139/chromebook-htop.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a>\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c68f81d78b4ca505831c771ccd325b63/95139/chromebook-myadmin.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.22254758418741%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"myadmin\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c68f81d78b4ca505831c771ccd325b63/f570d/chromebook-myadmin.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c68f81d78b4ca505831c771ccd325b63/0783d/chromebook-myadmin.png 240w,\n/static/c68f81d78b4ca505831c771ccd325b63/782f4/chromebook-myadmin.png 480w,\n/static/c68f81d78b4ca505831c771ccd325b63/f570d/chromebook-myadmin.png 960w,\n/static/c68f81d78b4ca505831c771ccd325b63/95139/chromebook-myadmin.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>终端模拟器是用的chrome的一个插件叫做crosh window</p>\n<p>linux虚拟机是用crouton安装的ubuntu16.04 core,可惜是共享内核的，所以ubuntu的内核也是3.10.18的</p>\n<p>一些常用工具包括：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>fish，我最喜欢的shell</li>\n<li>tmux，终端复用软件，可以开启多个会话</li>\n<li>ss，用来上网的，开启之后chromebook也可以共享上网，真不错</li>\n<li>emacs，我最爱的编辑器，之前crouton遇到最大的问题是中文输入法，有了emacs之后我可以用自带的pyim来输入中文了，没必要使用chromebook自带的输入法</li>\n<li>开发环境，nginx, mysql, php7, python, rvm等等之类的</li>\n<li>数据库连接是用一个叫做myadmin的chrome扩展实现的</li>\n</ol>\n<p>遇到的问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>cpu性能太差劲，我的lenovon21用的cpu是intel n2840的，一款低功耗的arm架构双核cpu，在打开多个浏览器标签时资源使用率总是达到100%，我在编译代码的时候就更费劲了，昨晚编译hakyll花了1个多小时，用公司的thinkpad t440s编译大概10分钟能搞定</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>显示器太渣，现在应该没有720p的笔记本显示器了吧，看着觉得很糢糊</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>机身是黑色塑料的，看起来很廉价，没有chromebook pixel和mac book pro那么银光闪闪</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>还是cpu太差劲，平时敲代码打字都有明显的卡顿了</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>总结一下：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>google是一家非常伟大的公司，感谢他们发明了chromebook这么伟大的产品</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>联想是美帝良心企业，在国内就买不到chromebook，国内的thinkpad价格也要比美帝高出一截</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>n21还算是一款性价比非常好的本子，就是性能有点弱，17年再换一个16年出的二手chromebook玩玩</p>\n</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/my-chromebook-review/","tagSlugs":["/tag/chromebook/","/tag/linux/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2016-06-05","description":"今年2月份附近入手的一台二手chromebook，到目前为止已经用了很长一段时间了，打算写一篇文章来总结一下使用体验...","tags":["Chromebook","Linux"],"title":"我的chromebook"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/my-chromebook-review/"}}}